                        <interp inst="t18400511-1507-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 13.—
<rs id="t18400511-1507-punishment-173" type="punishmentDescription">
